the consequence for minor offenses are:

First offense - verbal warning and counceling
second offense Written Warning and reflective essay 
Third offense  Community service 5-10 hours and parental notification
fourth offense Short term suspension 1 - 3 days and mandatory workshop
fifth offense long term suspension 1 week and disciplinary probation

for major offense:

First offense 
if Academic Dishonesty - Failing grade for the course and mandatory ethics workshop
other major Offenses - Suspension (1 week to 1 month) and mandatory counceling

Second offense
if Academic Dishonesty - Suspension for 1 Semester
other major offenses -  Suspension (1 month to 1 semester) and extended counceling

third offense
if Academic Dishonesty - Expulsion
other major offenses - Expulsion and notification to authorities if applicable




